<div class="title">Enjoyed the 'Intellectual' Value</div>
<div class="substance">AMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Eric&Exact=1">Eric</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Eric. "Enjoyed the 'Intellectual' Value: An Experience with AMT (exp11224)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 25, 2002. erowid.org/exp/11224</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

